'''美银证券集团'''（{{lang|en|'''BofA Securities, Inc.'''}}）是[[美国银行|美国银行]]旗下企业与[[投资银行|投资银行]]业务部门，前身'''美银美林集团'''（{{lang|en|'''Bank of America Merrill Lynch'''}}）。<ref name=home>{{cite web|url=http://www.bankofamerica.com/index.cfm?page=corp|title=Corporate and Institutional|accessdate=2011-01-21|publisher=[[美国银行|美国银行]]| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20110129222519/http://www.bankofamerica.com/index.cfm?page=corp| archivedate= 2011-01-29 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl= no}}</ref> 它在[[资本市场|资本市场]]提供[[收购|收购]]与[[兼并|兼并]]、[[股权|股权]]与[[债务|债务]]等服务，以及[[借贷|借贷]]、[[信托|信托]]、[[风险管理|风险管理]]、[[咨询|咨询]]、清偿力与支付力管理等。<ref name=montag/> 它是透过2009年1月美国银行收购[[美林证券|美林证券]]，整合双方公司与投资银行业务而组成的新部门。

== 公司历史 ==
[[美国银行|美国银行]]完全收购[[美林证券|美林证券]]在2009年1月1日。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE5001EA20090101?pageNumber=1|title=Bank of America completes Merrill Lynch purchase|accessdate=2011-01-21|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]| date=2009-01-01}}</ref> 美国银行于2009年9月开始整合美银美林集团旗下公司及投资银行业务。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aeabXop5GEk4|title=Bank of America Rebrands Offices in New York, London Towers|accessdate=2012-05-29|publisher=[[彭博社|彭博社]]|date=2009-09-03|archive-date=2013-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105014531/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=aeabXop5GEk4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2010年4月，美银美林集团任命克里斯蒂安·迈斯纳（Christian Meissner）为欧洲、中东及非洲地区投资银行业务的主管。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSLDE63L1TE20100422|title=Top Nomura Middle East banker quits firm - source|accessdate=2011-01-21|publisher=路透社|date=2010-04-22|archive-date=2010-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100524033238/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSLDE63L1TE20100422|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年4月，美银美林集团将其旗下公司与投资银行业务整合为一个单独的部门。<ref>
{{cite news|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/2011/04/19/uk-bankofamerica-moves-idUKTRE73I1VE20110419|title=BofA combines investment bank divisions|accessdate=2012-05-11|publisher=路透社|date=2011-04-19}}</ref>

2013年10月，美银美林集团被《{{Link-en|银行家 (杂志)|The Banker|银行家}}》“投资银行奖”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thebanker.com/Awards/Investment-Banking-Awards/The-Banker-s-Investment-Banking-Awards-2013-the-winners|title=The Banker's Investment Banking Awards, 2013 – the winners|accessdate=2013-10-28|publisher=银行家|date=2013-10-03|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029202720/http://www.thebanker.com/Awards/Investment-Banking-Awards/The-Banker-s-Investment-Banking-Awards-2013-the-winners|dead-url=no}}</ref> 之年度最具创新力的投资银行。<ref>
{{cite news|url=http://newsroom.bankofamerica.com/press-releases/awards-and-recognition/bofa-merrill-receives-banker-magazines-top-global-award|title=BofA Merrill Receives The Banker Magazine’s Top Global Award|accessdate=2013-10-28|publisher=美银美林集团|date=2013-07|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029210958/http://newsroom.bankofamerica.com/press-releases/awards-and-recognition/bofa-merrill-receives-banker-magazines-top-global-award|archivedate=2013-10-29}}</ref>

